a two in one super cute natural hairstyle for the spring time. Lil side swoop action with bouncy curls. 

Tutorial:
1. Start with clean damp hair
2. Section off a piece in the front, twist it so it’s out of your way 
3. Define curls (water, @patternbeauty curl moose & wetline xtreme gel @xtremegelusa)
4. Smooth hair out with @patternbeauty shower brush & pin up
5.  Mix got2b hair gel (black tube) and got2b freeze spray together on a paper plate 
6. Untwist the front and apply the gel mixture in sections, smooth as you go 
7. Use @dysonhair supersonic blow dryer on cool to set into place 
8. Take the two sections and tie them together with a hair tie in back. 
9. Wrap the front in a scarf for a couple of hours and boom. You finished. 
The claw clip is from @patternbeauty for a lil razzle dazzle. 
#naturalhairstyles #blackgirlhairstyles #naturalhairtutorial
